cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image detection and uses YOLOv3 model for object detection.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a likely category as the paper deals with a dataset of more than 56k images of marine vessels.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a likely category as the paper uses a deep learning model for object detection.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with web-scraping to collect the dataset.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possible category as the paper deals with real-time target detection in maritime scenarios which may have security implications.
